td.p:
This request for a preliminary ruling concerns the interpretation of Article 32(3) of Regulation (EC) No 810/2009 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 13 July 2009 establishing a Community Code on Visas (
OJ 2009 L 243, p. 1
), as amended by Regulation (EU) No 610/2013 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 26 June 2013 (
OJ 2013 L 182, p. 1
) (‘the Visa Code’).
